281680.title: Sox: A Family's Best Friend

332933.title: Fred 3: Camp Fred

342067.description: A teenager who struggles to adjust to her new stepfamily and school receives some help when a dog training app gives her the power to control boys.

680747.title: Nativity 2: Danger in the Manger

682075.description: Tired of being bullied, Cassandra prays that her nemesis, Katie, the queen bee of social media, would know what it's like to walk a day in her shoes.

713193.description: Un joven adolescente compra una poci—n de crecimiento, pero resulta contraproducente.

715616.title: Alone in the Woods
715616.description: After climbing into the wrong van on the way to his grandma's cabin for Thanksgiving, ten-year-old Justin discovers he's riding with two kidnappers.

02405.title: Undercover High
02405.description: Undercover High is a half-hour, hidden camera show for teens, that takes the world of prank television and brings it to the one place that kids will never expect it - their own high school!

03855.title: Numb Chucks
03855.description: Two dim-witted woodchuck vigilantes try to be awesome and save the citizens of their land by using kung fu skills that they don't even have.

0300008637.title: Mike Tyson Mysteries
0300008637.description: The adult animation classic series featuring the voice talents of Mike Tyson and Norm MacDonald sees the champion boxer taking on weekly mysteries!

02101.title: Almost Naked Animals
02101.description: Even though the title may suggest otherwise, "Almost Naked Animals" is an animated series geared toward kids. The show's main setting is the Banana Cabana, a seemingly ordinary, run-of-the-mill beachfront hotel. What's not ordinary about the hotel is who (or what) runs it -- animals who are all shaved and wearing underwear. The Banana Cabana's top dog is Howie, who would barely be able to keep things under control without his crew helping him out. That crew includes jittery desk clerk Octo, sugary-sweet activities director Bunny and duck-of-all-trades Duck.

04835.title: Talking Tom and Friends Minis
04835.description: The funny friends bring a sense of adventure to their everyday world, where even the most ordinary things have the potential to be extraordinary.

04373.title: Verano Azul
04373.description: Esta serie trata sobre las aventuras de un grupo de jovenes durante sus vacaciones de verano en una pequena ciudad en la costa sur de Espana. Los siete ninos: Quique, Javi, Pancho, Bea, Desi, Tito y Pirana, conocen a dos adultos con quienes comparten muchas experiencias nuevas, Julia, una pintora, y Chanquete, un marinero retirado que vive en un bote en un barco. cumbre.

0300007838.title: Felix the Cat
0300007838.description: Laugh along with a charming cartoon cat who, thanks in part to his magic bag, always manages to stay one step ahead of his wicked professor foe.

04364.title: SheZow
04364.description: An extreme 12-year-old with an attitude inherits his late aunt’s ring and turns him into a female superhero with comic results.

03348.title: Super Mario Bros. Super Show!
03348.description: A pair of plumbers get sucked into a magical kingdom, where a beautiful princess needs their help to stop a wicked reptile bent on destruction.

01084.title: Debra!
01084.description: The funny and vibrant live action series DEBRA! follows an energetic girl named Debra Carnegie Cameron Delong who has a mission to improve the world. Have you seen the World? Its big and amazing, but with an injection of teen enthusiasm it could be perfect!  Debra applies her big imagination to improving her school, her community and her friends lives while she is on a mission to bring back a stronger sense of community to Camfield.

03667.title: Rocket Monkeys
03667.description: Brother monkeys take on vital intergalactic missions, causing more mischief than they prevent, with the aid of an outdated robot and a space octopus.

0300005179.title: 3 Amigonauts
0300005179.description: Three friends in the far-off future go to the best space academy in the solar system and find themselves in far-out adventures all the time!

0300010076.title: Eight Is Enough
0300010076.description: This touching series follows a close-knit family as they face the hardships and challenges of the ups and downs of everyday life in a family of ten.

02.title: Jem
02.description: Using holograms, Jerrica and her pals become Jem and the Holograms, battling other bands like the Misfits and the Stingers, to keep the Starlight foundation going!

04082.title: The Real McCoys
04082.description: Amos McCoy moves his family to an inherited farm in California, where he's quick to give advice to his grandchildren and his neighbors.

0300008442.title: ALF
0300008442.description: The hit ‘80s comedy about a furry alien life form – ALF – who crashes into a suburban family’s house and takes his place there as a total smart-aleck.

02365.title: Pelswick (Español)
02365.description: A este muchacho se le deslizan las amenazas de los bullies de su escuela. Es que es un experto en el arte de deslizarse, pues anda en silla de ruedas.

0300005045.title: My Uncle Silas
0300005045.description: A boisterous uncle takes care of his 10-year-old nephew for the summer in this turn-of-the-century drama.

04532.title: Chicken Girls
04532.description: Rhyme and her friends—known by their 'ship name, "The Chicken Girls"—have been dancing together forever. But this year, everything's changing...

0300004899.title: Some Assembly Required
0300004899.description: A 14-year-old running a toy company hires a group of his friends to help him create amazing new toys.

0300008259.title: The Little Rascals Best of Our Gang (In Color)
0300008259.description: Join Spanky, Alfalfa, Buckwheat, Stymie, and Porky as they pal around, going on adventures and learning about the world together.

04577.title: Family Affair
04577.description: An American classic sitcom about Bill, an engineer, who must share his NYC apartment with three unexpected children and his valet, Mr. French.

0300008446.title: The Baby-Sitters Club
0300008446.description: The beloved story of a young girl and her group of friends as they share their struggles balancing school work, babysitting, and growing up.

0300008471.title: Andy and the Band
0300008471.description: If Andy and the Odd Socks keep getting roped into outlandish errands for their super fans, they’re never going to make it to their gigs on time.

0300007091.title: The Wannabes
0300007091.description: This comedy sitcom follows six performing art school tweens who "wanna be" pop stars, even if it they have to dressing up like fruit and rocking out in a local cafe.

03043.title: My Goldfish Is Evil
03043.description: There's no pet easier than a goldfish. Unless he's Admiral Bubbles, whose attempts to conquer the world keep life interesting for his young owner.

0300006856.title: The Flintstones
0300006856.description: Laugh along with the classic misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families living amongst dinosaurs, doing their best in prehistoric times.

0300008345.title: Calvin and the Colonel
0300008345.description: For 26 episodes on primetime TV, Amos ‘n’ Andy was reborn as an animated series with the main characters presented as a sly fox and dimwitted bear.

02089.title: Best Ed
02089.description:
Best Ed is about the unlikely friendship between a dog named Ed and a squirrel named Buddy. Ed wakes up every morning to be the best Ed he can be, even though it drives Buddy bonkers. But for every funny blunder Buddy suffers, thanks to Ed’s cloying good deeds, Buddy knows that…although it’s hard to live with Ed…it’s harder to live without him. They’re not just friends, they’re best friends.
Meet the new odd couple for kids…one best Buddy. And one Best Ed!

015.title: Littlest Pet Shop
015.description: Blythe lives in the big city, right above the Littlest Pet Shop, a day-camp for all types of pets. When she discovers she can talk to the animals, the adventure begins!

0300009312.title: Funniest Pets & People
0300009312.description: This series features hysterical, fast-paced video clips submitted by viewers who share the funniest moments of their favorite pets & people.

02175.title: In Your Dreams
02175.description: Australian teenage twins, Samantha and Ben Hazelton discover what ‘culture shock’ is all about when they spend the summer with their eccentric, aristocratic and accident prone relatives who live in a remote German castle.

0300009144.title: ALF: The Animated Series
0300009144.description: Follow the adventures and misadventures of ALF, under the real name Gordon Shumway, on his home planet of Melmac before he crash landed on Earth.

0386.title: The Weird Al Show
0386.description: Yankovics signature warped comedy, original songs, TV and movie spoofs, offbeat animation, and ability to attract a wonderful and motley collection of special surprise guests are what made The Weird Al Show a Saturday morning hit.

0300009952.title: Moesha
0300009952.description: The everyday life of Moesha Mitchell, a vivacious young woman juggling romance, college, ever-changing family dynamics, and friendships.

01791.title: Pigs Next Door
01791.description: When a farmer decides to move, he gives his land to his loyal pigs: father Phil, mother Clara and their two little piglets, Chuckie and April. But Phil, feeling himself drawn to a higher calling, insists on offering his children the chance of a good education, so he persuades his family to sell the farm and move to the city. No sooner said than done and before long the pig family have settled into their new surroundings. Phil finds a job as a car salesman, while Clara gets interested in fashion and the kids of course go to school. You wouldn’t notice anything out of the ordinary if it weren't for the fact they’re the only pigs in the neighbourhood, an area inhabited, exclusively, by human beings!

0300004982.title: Sunnyside Up
0300004982.description: After coming to a new high school, Lily and her newfound friends form an unconventional girl gang.

0300007032.title: 6teen
0300007032.description: This sharp and amusing mid-00s animated comedy follows the after-school lives of six 16 year-old mall-rats.

01098.title: Sabrina: The Animated Series
01098.description: In the town of Greendale lives Sabrina, a half mortal and half witch who often uses spells to wreak middle school havoc.

02176.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
02176.description: Bean is back! Join him, alongside his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady, for more zany mishaps that surround his daily life.

0300005651.title: Just Kidding
0300005651.description: This hidden-camera show features over a dozen kids who come up with hilarious and quirky pranks to pull on adults who have no idea what’s going on!

03857.title: Nerds & Monsters
03857.description: A group of nerdy middle school friends and one jock end up as castaways on an unknown island that’s home to dumb monsters who don't like them at all.

0300007398.title: Tukiti Crecí De Una
0300007398.description: Antonio tiene 15 años y, al regresar de la escuela, tiene que cuidar a su hermano Pipo de 6 años para que su mamá, Mildred, pueda trabajar.

03948.title: Spike Team
03948.description: An evil town ruler removes all greenery and she wants one last piece of land, but a volleyball team of 6 girls plan to play her team and win it back.

0300005056.title: Mortified
0300005056.description: An imaginative young girl uses her vivid creativity to fantasize and escape the pressures of school and avoid the embarrassment of her parents.
